string.value: You're back in the present and the Future Doctor Bing has sent you a message.\r\n(How did he send a message?)

The Future Doctor Bing wants you to meet his present self.
Use the Command Center Warp Capsule #i2030011# to warp to the Omega Sector.

Find Doctor Bing, who is somewhere inside.
Doctor Bing is hard at work and doesn't seem to have any idea what's going on.\r\n\r\n(Yet...)
I'm relieved. Everything has returned to normal! I guess this will be the last time we see each other.\r\nBut...
Who knows what stupid things the me in your present time will do now? Right about now...he should be at the Omega Sector.
Can you please go see him one last time and make sure he's okay? He probably won't remember you...
Thank you! I will give you the Command Center Warp Capsule. Please use it.
What are you thinking? Fine. Do as you will...
What is it? I'm just a researcher. If you're a Mesoranger recruit, go see Chury!\r\n#L0##bHey, what do you know about time travel?#l\n#k

Are you kidding me!? I have so much research to do, I don't even have time to sleep. Bah, who has time to worry about time travel.
Now, please. Don't bother me.
#L0##b(Hmm... I guess he doesn't have time to re-make the same mistakes.)#l
#k
Anyway, I'll see you around!\n\r(I've thought of something much more interesting than Time Machines... Heh, heh, heh.)
